title: Youtube Channel For Support Mains  *EN INGLES*

embed.description: Hey! I am a support main on League of Legends. I play on the LAS server as I live in Chile but I am originally from England. I will be uploading support game...

body:
*I'M SPEAKING IN ENGLISH BECAUSE I AM FROM ENGLAND BUT I LIVE IN CHILE NOW AND PLAY ON LAS*
I created a YouTube channel for support mains, where I display gameplays of mine with an intro commentary and music. 
This content is aimed at support mains who are bronze or silver as my peak in lol is Gold 1. 
Season 7 was my first season playing League and I got to Silver 2 and got to Gold 1 in pre season 8, this season I am aiming for Platinum/Diamond. 
If any supports would like to learn from watching replays/gameplay then please feel free to check it out. 
I posted this channel before and the response from the community was really good! 
So Thank you for the support and there will much more content coming! 
I will start to do live commentaries soon!

replies.body: Uh, could you stop posting the same over and over? :S If you're looking for English-speaking players, this is not the place.
